===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|fr|restaurant}}, present participle of the verb {{m|fr|restaurer}}, corresponding to {{der|en|la|restaurans|restaurans, restaurantis}}, present participle of {{m|la|restauro||I restore}}, from the name of the 'restorative' soup served in the first establishments.

